    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really nervous to call the doctor because i don't want them to think i can't handle the meds and take them away. if i just keep drinking water and wait it out for like 24 hours, it'll probably just pass right, right? it's probably just my body adjusting to the new pill.",
